  "Remove C22 (10µF), C23 (0.1µF), C24 near the X-MIN header. GY-GPSV3 is 3.3V only. Alternative: Serial2 (GPIO16 RX, GPIO17 TX) — no cap removal but conflicts with Axis4 focuser. Config: TIME_LOCATION_SOURCE GPS, SERIAL_GPS_BAUD 9600.": "Retirez C22 (10µF), C23 (0,1µF), C24 près de l'en-tête X-MIN. Le GY-GPSV3 est en 3,3V uniquement. Alternative : Serial2 (GPIO16 RX, GPIO17 TX) — pas de retrait de condensateur mais conflit avec le focuser de l'Axe4. Config : TIME_LOCATION_SOURCE GPS, SERIAL_GPS_BAUD 9600.",
